author: Hannah Miller
title: Maine institutes 'stay healthy at home' order during coronavirus outbreak
description: Maine became the latest state Tuesday to order residents to remain at home during the coronavirus pandemic.
content: Maine became the latest state Tuesday to order residents to remain at home during the coronavirus pandemic. It joins New York, New Jersey, California and Washington  all among the hardest hit by the spread of COVID-19  in limiting residents' movements to curb… [+1417 chars]
